message_text: Sorry to hear that you are finding this challenging! Try summarising what someone has said before responding: “What I hear you saying is…”. This will show them that you have listened to what they said and also gives them the chance to clarify anything that may have been misunderstood. This helps build effective communication skills.
It is completely normal to experience this. Looking after family is difficult and can be tiresome. Try sharing your responsibilities with your household!
